<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Agri-Energy Connect</h1>
    <p class="lead mt-4">
        Bridging sustainable agriculture and green energy innovation in South Africa.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-4" />

    <p class="fs-5">
        Agri-Energy Connect is a forward-thinking digital platform designed to empower farmers, green energy experts, and agricultural innovators.
        Our mission is to build a collaborative ecosystem that accelerates the adoption of sustainable farming methods and renewable energy solutions across the agricultural sector.
    </p>

    <p class="fs-5">
        With a focus on accessibility, knowledge sharing, and real-world impact, this platform provides tools and resources to help users:
    </p>

    <ul class="text-start mx-auto" style="max-width: 800px;">
        <li><strong>Discover sustainable farming practices</strong> through our interactive hub and expert-driven discussions.</li>
        <li><strong>Browse and compare green energy solutions</strong> tailored for agricultural applications in our dedicated marketplace.</li>
        <li><strong>Access educational resources</strong> such as webinars, training modules, and courses on renewable integration in farming.</li>
        <li><strong>Collaborate on projects</strong> and explore funding opportunities aimed at eco-conscious agricultural initiatives.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="fs-5">
        Whether you're a smallholder farmer looking to reduce your environmental impact, or an energy provider seeking meaningful partnerships, Agri-Energy Connect is your gateway to innovation, sustainability, and progress.
    </p>

    
</div>
